msgstr ".380子弹的空弹壳。"

#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid ".303 British"
msgid_plural ".303 Britishs"
msgstr[0] ".303英国"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '.303 British'}
#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid ""
".303 British was commonly used before the introduction and standardization "
"of NATO-bloc ammunition. It is roughly similar to 7.62x51mm in terms of "
"ballistics, but is rimmed."
msgstr ".303英国弹在引入和标准化北约集团弹药之前被广泛使用。它在弹道学上大致类似于7.62x51mm，但有底缘。"

#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid ".303 casing"
msgid_plural ".303 casings"
msgstr[0] ".303弹壳"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '.303 casing'}
#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid "An empty casing from a .303 round."
msgstr ".303子弹的空弹壳。"

#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid "reloaded .303 British"
msgid_plural "reloaded .303 Britishs"
msgstr[0] "重装.303英国弹"

#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid "Match 7.62x51mm"
msgid_plural "Match 7.62x51mms"
msgstr[0] "比赛级7.62x51mm"

#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid "7.62x54mmR API/Explosive"
msgid_plural "7.62x54mmR API/Explosives"
msgstr[0] "7.62x54mmR API/爆炸弹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '7.62x54mmR API/Explosive'}
#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid ""
"Originally used by Soviet Anti-Air weapons, then used by snipers to blow "
"apart fascist light armour. Now used by you. Careful using it too close to "
"yourself. "
msgstr "最初用于苏联防空武器，后来被狙击手用来炸开法西斯轻型装甲。现在由你使用。注意不要离自己太近使用。"

#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid ".460 Rowland"
msgid_plural ".460 Rowland"
msgstr[0] ".460罗兰"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '.460 Rowland', 'str_pl': '.460 Rowland'}
#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid ""
"The .460 Rowland is a modified version of the .45 round used in pistols like"
" the M1911. The .460 is an evolutionary step as it has more power and faster"
" velocity then the .45 making it one of the most powerful semi-automatic "
"pistol round in the world."
msgstr ""
".460罗兰是用于M1911等手枪的.45子弹的改进版本。.460是进化的一步，因为它比.45拥有更大的威力和更快的速度，使其成为世界上最强大的半自动手枪弹之一。"

#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid "reloaded .460 Rowland"
msgid_plural "reloaded .460 Rowland"
msgstr[0] "重装.460罗兰弹"

#: .\art_ammo.json
