msgid_plural "8mm Mausers"
msgstr[0] "8mm毛瑟"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '8mm Mauser'}
#: .\art_ammo.json
msgid ""
"Introduced in its current form in 1903, the 8mm Mauser is one of the most "
"famous and prolific cartridges of all time. Its users stretched from China "
"to Chile, and is still used today."
msgstr "8毫米毛瑟弹于1903年以当前形式问世，是有史以来最著名且产量最大的弹药之一。其使用范围从中国延伸至智利，至今仍在使用。"

